Introduction

The purpose of this tutorial is to provide a strong base knowledge of the kidney to work off of. This tutorial will include sections of the kidney chapter of ‘Medical Physiology’ by Walter F. Boron and Emile L. Boulpaep. It will also include a link to a short quiz to check your knowledge. After taking the quiz, the correct answers and feedback should be available for review. This tutorial will also include supplemental materials that may be helpful for the reader
